```WEBVTT

00:00.720 --> 00:02.320
<v Agent>Hello, thank you for calling Contoso.

00:02.320 --> 00:03.440
<v Agent>Who am I speaking with today?

00:04.480 --> 00:06.080
<v Customer>Hi, my name is Mary Rondo.

00:06.120 --> 00:07.920
<v Customer>I'm trying to enroll myself with Contoso.

00:09.520 --> 00:09.920
<v Agent>Hi, Mary.

00:10.280 --> 00:11.880
<v Agent>Are you calling because you need health insurance?

00:13.040 --> 00:13.360
<v Customer>Yes.

00:13.520 --> 00:15.080
<v Customer>Yeah, I'm calling to sign up for insurance.

00:15.920 --> 00:16.240
<v Agent>Great.

00:16.240 --> 00:19.200
<v Agent>Uh If you can answer a few questions, we can get you signed up in a Jiffy.

00:20.160 --> 00:20.360
<v Customer>Okay.

00:21.760 --> 00:22.880
<v Agent>So what's your full name?

00:24.600 --> 00:33.440
<v Customer>Uh So Mary Beth Rondo, last name is R like Romeo, O like Ocean, N like Nancy D, D like Dog, and O like Ocean again.

00:34.320 --> 00:34.800
<v Customer>Rondo.

00:36.000 --> 00:36.320
<v Agent>Got it.

00:37.080 --> 00:40.000
<v Agent>And what's the best callback number in case we get disconnected?

00:41.600 --> 00:43.360
<v Customer>I only have a cell phone, so I can give you that.

00:44.160 --> 00:44.960
<v Agent>Yep, that'll be fine.

00:46.240 --> 00:46.560
<v Customer>Sure.

00:46.560 --> 00:53.760
<v Customer>So it's 234-554 and then 9312.

00:54.800 --> 00:55.200
<v Agent>Got it.

00:55.200 --> 00:58.920
<v Agent>So to confirm, it's 234-554-9312.

01:00.000 --> 01:00.640
<v Customer>Yep, that's right.

01:01.680 --> 01:02.160
<v Agent>Excellent.

01:02.720 --> 01:05.840
<v Agent>Let's get some additional information for your application.

01:06.320 --> 01:07.080
<v Agent>Do you have a job?

01:07.080 --> 01:07.120
<v Agent>Uh.

01:08.680 --> 01:10.000
<v Customer>Yes, I am self-employed.

01:11.200 --> 01:13.520
<v Agent>Okay, so then you have a social security number as well?

01:14.720 --> 01:15.200
<v Customer>Uh Yes, I do.

01:16.200 --> 01:18.600
<v Agent>Okay, and what is your social security number, please?

01:18.600 --> 01:18.760
<v Agent>Uh Sure.

01:20.000 --> 01:22.320
<v Customer>So it's 412-253-4931.

01:24.800 --> 01:26.080
<v Customer>6789.

01:27.120 --> 01:29.680
<v Agent>Sorry, was that a 25 or a 225?

01:29.680 --> 01:30.720
<v Agent>You cut out for a bit.

01:32.160 --> 01:37.320
<v Customer>It's double two, so 412, then another two, then five.

01:38.720 --> 01:39.440
<v Agent>Thank you so much.

01:40.400 --> 01:43.040
<v Agent>And could I have your e-mail address, please?

01:44.240 --> 01:47.440
<v Customer>Yeah, it's maryrondo@gmail.com.

01:47.520 --> 01:49.600
<v Customer>So my first and last name at gmail.com.

01:49.760 --> 01:51.280
<v Customer>No periods, no dashes.

01:52.800 --> 01:53.120
<v Agent>Great.

01:53.640 --> 01:55.040
<v Agent>Uh That is the last question.

01:55.040 --> 01:58.880
<v Agent>So let me take your information and I'll be able to get you signed up right away.

01:59.400 --> 02:03.040
<v Agent>Thank you for calling Contoso and I'll be able to get you signed up immediately.

02:03.440 --> 02:07.520
<v Agent>One of our agents will call you back in about 24 hours or so to confirm your application.

02:08.640 --> 02:09.120
<v Customer>That sounds good.

02:09.480 --> 02:09.800
<v Customer>Thank you.

02:11.200 --> 02:11.760
<v Agent>Absolutely.

02:12.160 --> 02:18.480
<v Agent>If you need anything else, please give us a call at 1-800-555-5564, extension 123.

02:19.240 --> 02:20.960
<v Agent>Thank you very much for calling Contoso.

02:22.320 --> 02:24.160
<v Customer>Actually, so I have one more question.

02:25.080 --> 02:25.680
<v Agent>Yes, of course.

02:27.120 --> 02:30.000
<v Customer>I'm curious, will I be getting a physical card as proof of coverage?

02:31.440 --> 02:36.400
<v Agent>So the default is a digital membership card, but we can send you a physical card if you prefer.

02:37.880 --> 02:38.320
<v Customer>Uh Yes.

02:38.320 --> 02:39.760
<v Customer>Could you please mail it to me when it's ready?

02:39.760 --> 02:42.320
<v Customer>I'd like to have it shipped to, are you ready for my address?

02:43.640 --> 02:43.920
<v Agent>Uh Yeah.

02:45.080 --> 02:54.720
<v Customer>Uh So it's 2660 Unit A on Maple Avenue, Southeast Lansing, and then zip code is 48823.

02:56.240 --> 02:56.800
<v Agent>Absolutely.

02:57.000 --> 02:58.080
<v Agent>I've made a note on your file.

02:59.560 --> 02:59.840
<v Customer>Awesome.

02:59.840 --> 03:00.400
<v Customer>Thanks so much.

03:01.520 --> 03:02.240
<v Agent>You're very welcome.

03:02.320 --> 03:04.160
<v Agent>Thank you for calling Contoso and have a great day.```

Summary.valueString: Mary Rondo called Contoso to enroll in health insurance. The agent collected her personal information, including her full name, phone number, social security number, and email address. Mary requested a physical membership card, and the agent noted her mailing address for this purpose. The agent confirmed that an agent would call back within 24 hours to confirm her application.
